Aṃbikā  (II)--a daughter of the King of Kāśi and wife of Vicitravīrya. 1) Bhā. IX. 22. 24. Vi. IV. 20. 36. Mother of Dhṛtarāṣṭṛa. 2) Bhā. X. 48. 34.

