अयोमुख
Ayomukha  (II)--Mt. a hill with medicinal herbs. M. 163. 71.

अयोमुखी
Ayomukhī  (I)--a mother goddess. M. 179. 29.

अयोमुखी
Ayomukhī  (II)--the wife of Vighna. Br. III. 59. 13; Vā. 84. 13.

