अग्निहोत्र
Agnihotra  Ṛsis procreate for the world and establish Dharma in it; live in the Pitṛyāna. Gṛhamedhi Rṣis; 88,000; live in the southern path of the sun till the end of the world; 4) M. 124. 98-100, 102-4. quality of immanence in them; kinds of; 5) Vā. 5. 35; 49. 126; 59. 63. place of 8000 sages. 6) Br. II. 7. 180. Ṛṣi--Paramaṛṣi, Ṛṣitā, Mahaṛṣis, Ṛṣikas, Ṛṣiputrakas, Śrutaṛṣis and Ṛṣijāti, ety. of. Vā. 59. 79-87.

