Kaśyapa  (II)--a sage and contemporary of Kṛṣṇa. Invited for Yudhiṣṭhira's Rājasūya. 1) Bhā. X. 74. 9. Came to Syamantapañcaka to see Kṛṣṇa; 2) Ib. X. 84. 4. one of the sages who left for Piṇḍāraka; 3) Ib. XI. 1. 12. met by Takṣaka on his way to Parīkṣit. 4) Ib. XII. 6. 11.

