Kāmaśāstra --In Sairandhri's house there were pictures drawn according to prescriptions of Kāmaśāstra: 1) Bhā. X. 48. [2]; M. 220. 2. a treatise by Bābhravya, a Pāñcāla. 2) M. 21. 30.

