Kṛṣṇaveṇā(i) --R. A mahānadi from the Sahya hills --sacred to Pitṛs; 1) Br. II. 12. 14; 16. 34; M. 51. 13; Vā. 108. 81; Vi. II. 3. 12. personified as a wife of Havyavāhana fire. 2) M. 22. 46; 114. 29; 163. 61; Vā. 29. 13.

