Gopati  (II)--the name of Viṣṇu in Gayā. Vā. 108. 52.

गोपति
Gopati  (III)--Māyā, the Vaiṣṇavī in Gayā worshipped by Rudra. Vā. 108. 52.

गोपद
Gopada --a Tuṣita god. Br. II. 36. 10.

गोपन
Gopanas --Ātreya gotrakaras. M. 197. 3.

