देवल
Devala  (II)--a son of Pratyūṣa and father of two sons; 1) Br. III. 3. 27; Vā. 66. 26; Vi. I. 15. 117. a Vasava. 2) M. 5. 27; 203. 7. 

देवल
Devala  (III)--a son of Asita and Ekaparṇā; 1) Br. III. 8. 32; 10. 19; Vā. 70. 27; 72. 17. a Brahmavādin and the best among the Śāṇḍilyas. 2) Br. II. 32. 113; III. 8. 32; Vā. 59. 103; 70. 28.

