Devala  (IV)--a son of Vasudeva and Upadevī; (Śiśirāvatī-Br. P.). Br. III. 71. 182; M. 46. 17.

देवल
Devala  (V)--father of Sannati, a queen of Brahmadatta, the Pāñcāla king. M. 20. 26.

