Parameṣṭhi  (IV)--married the daughter of Dakṣa and became the father of Nārada. Br. III. 2. 13-18.

परंतप
Paraṃtapa --a son of Tāmasa Manu. M. 9. 17.

परवृत्
Paravṛt --a son of Rukmakavaca and father of five sons. Vi. IV. 12. 10-11.

परशव
Paraśavas --a tribe. Vā. 99. 268. 

परशु
Paraśu  (I)--a son of Uttama Manu. Br. II. 36. 39; Vi. III. 1. 15.

