Parāsikas --people constituting the cavalry forces of Lalitā. Br. IV. 16. 16.

पराहत
Parāhata --from the region of planets to that of ṛṣis or sages; the sixth skandha. Vā. 67. 119. 

परिकम्पिनी
Parikampinī --a mind-born mother. M. 179. 24.

परिकूट
Parikūṭa --a Trayārṣeya. M. 198. 10.

