Pariplava --the son of Sukhīnala and father of Sunaya. Bhā. IX. 22. 42.

परिप्लुत
Paripluta --the son of Sukhībala. Vā. 99. 275.

परिमति
Parimati --a Bhavya God. Br. II. 36. 72.

परिवन्
Parivan --one of the seven seers of the Svārociṣa epoch. Vi. III. 1. 11.

