Bṛhat  (I)--Sāmans having the metrical form of Bṛhatī; for śrāddha; 1) M. 17. 38. in connection with installing a new image. 2) Ib. 265. 27.

बृहत्
Bṛhat  (II)--a son of Mantraśarīra. Vā. 67. 5.

