मृत्यु
Mṛtyu  (VII)--the Lord of Death; born out of the eyes of Brahmā; 1) M. 3. 11; 213. 4. had an ugly daughter Sunīthā married to AngaPrajāpati; 2) Ib. 10. 3. an assistant to Yama. 3) Ib. 213. 18.

मृत्यु
Mṛtyu  (VIII)--a mind-born mother. M. 179. 15.

मृत्युञ्जय
Mṛtyuñjaya --is Śiva. Br. IV. 36. 19.

मृदङ्ग
Mṛdaṅga --a musical instrument. Vā. 45. 40. 

