Megha  (I)--a Rākṣasa in Sutalam. Br. II. 20. 22; Vā. 50. 22.

मेघ
Megha  (II)--formed out of the shell of Brahmā's egg, cosmology of clouds and rain; waters taken in by the rays of the sun and let out as showers; served by the wind. M. 2. 33; 125. 16-35.

