Vasuman  (VI)--with Aṣṭaka, Pratardana and Śibi, all grandsons of Yayāti by his daughter, performed a sacrifice and in that hall Yayāti fallen from heaven, spoke with them and went back to heaven; 1) M. 35. 5. discourse of, with Yayāti on different things of heaven; 2) Ib. 38. 22; 41. 18; 42. 1f. went to heaven with the above. 3) Ib. 42. 14, 26 and 28.

