Vasumitra --a son of Sujyeṣṭha (Vasujyeṣṭha-M. P.) and father of Bhadraka (Udanka-Vi. P.); ruled for ten years. Bhā. XII. 1. 17; Br. III. 74. 152; M. 272. 28; Vā. 99. 339; Vi. IV. 24. 35.

