Vidas --a Bhārgava branch. Br. III. 1. 100.

विदर्भ
Vidarbha  (I) (c)--a kingdom to which the Yadus migrated. 1) Bhā. IV. 28. 28; X. 2. 3; Br. III. 49. 1. Its capital Kuṇḍina, visited by Kṛṣṇa. 2) Bhā. X. 53. 6-7; Vi. V. 26. 1 Its king went to Syamantapañcaka for the solar eclipse. 3) Bhā. X. 82. 13.

