Vidiśa --a particular locality between the Cakra (Candra-Vā. P.) and Maināka hills towards the south. Here is Samvartaka fire swallowing waters as also Aurva and Vaḍavāmukha. Br. II. 18. 79. Vā. 47. 75-6. 

