Vidyā  (I)--leads to happiness: Role of teacher and pupil. A means to attain final beatitude; 1) Bhā. XI. 10. 12; 11. 4-7; VI. 16. 27. of 18 groups--also 14 groups; 2) Br. III. 35. 88-9; III. 15. 29; IV. 12. 57; 18. 46; 34. 69. survive antarkṣaya. 3) M. 2. 13.

