Vidhātri  (I)--a son of Khyātī and Bhṛgu, married Niyatī, (Āyatī-Vā. P.) a daughter of Meru. His place in the Siśumāra; father of Pāṇḍu. Bhā. IV. 1. 43-4; V. 23. 5; Br. II. 13. 37; 11. 6; Vā. 28. 1; 30. 34.

