विनता
Vinatā  (II)--a mother goddess. M. 179. 19.

विनताश्व
Vinatāśva --a son of Sudyumna, became the lord of western territories. Vā. 85. 19.

विनय
Vinaya  (I)--a son of Lajjā. Br. II. 9. 61; Vā. 10. 36.

