Sannati  (III)--a daughter of Dakṣa; wife of Kratu (Marīci-Vi. P.) (see also Santati and Samtati); 1) Vā. 10. 28, 31; Vi. I. 7. 7, 25. sons, Vālakhilya sages, 6000 in number. 2) Br. II. 9. 52; 11. 36.

