Samyogajam --a sin of four kinds; the doer, the aid, cause of action and approver; each ten times greater than the other. Br. IV. 8. 39-40.

सम्रम्भ
Samrambha --one of the names in the fourth Marut gaṇa. Vā. 67. 127.

