Sindhuretā --the kingdom of. M. 121. 48.

सिन्धुसौवीर
Sindhusauvīra--(c)  the country over which Rahūgaṇa ruled. Bhā. V. 10. 1; M. 114. 41; Vā. 45. 116.

सिम्ह
Simha  (I)--a son of Mādrī and Kṛṣṇa. Bhā. X. 61. 15.

सिम्ह
Simha  (II)--a palace in the form of a lion; the toraṇa is 16 hastas. M. 269. 36, 49.

