Simhadvāra --the lion-gate in front of Śivaloka. Br. III. 32. 11.

सिम्हनाद
Simhanāda  (also meghanāda) a war cry; 1) Br. IV. 29. 28; made by Kṛṣṇa on seeing the Ariṣṭa bull; 2) Vi. V. 14. 8. before wrestling with Cāṇūra. 3) Ib. V. 20. 35. 

सिम्हरथ
Simharatha --the chariot of lion of Kārttikeya. Vā. 41. 38.

