Simhāsana --the lion throne for kings; 1) Br. III. 26. 21. of Devī which was placed in the Sabhā; 2) Ib. IV. 14. 12. of the Pāṇḍavas; Mārkaṇḍeya seated by Yudhiṣṭhira on; 3) M. 103. 18. of Tāraka Asura. 4) Ib. 148. 29;

