Suketu  (I)--a son of Nandivardhana of Magadha, and father of Devarāta; a bold and righteous king. Bhā. IX. 13. 14; Br. III. 64. 7; Vā. 89. 7; Vi. IV. 5. 25. Br. III. 64. 7.

