Suketu  (III)--a Dānava. Br. III. 6. 6; Vā. 68. 6.

सुकेतु
Suketu  (IV)--a Vānara chief. Br. III. 7. 243.

सुकेतु
Suketu  (V)--a son of Sagara. Br. III. 63. 147.

सुकेतु
Suketu  (VI)--a son of Ketumān: father of Dharmaketu. Br. III. 67. 74.

सुकेतु
Suketu  (VII)--a son of Sunītha; a righteous monarch; father of Dharmaketu. Vā. 92. 69-70; Vi. IV. 8. 19.

सुकेश
Sukeśa  (I)--a sage in Dāruvana. Br. II. 27. 104.

सुकेश
Sukeśa  (II)--a Dānava. Br. III. 61. 9; Vā. 68. 9.

सुकेष
Sukeṣa  (III)--a Mt. Br. III. 7. 453. 

