Sukha  (I)--born of Śānti. Bhā. IV. 1. 51.

सुख
Sukha  (II)--a son of Siddhi. Br. II. 9. 61; Vā. 10. 37.

सुख
Sukha  (III)--a son of Śuki and Garuḍa. Br. III. 7. 450.

