Sukhīnala --a son of Nṛcakṣu and father of Pariplava. Bhā. IX. 22. 41. 2.

सुखीबल
Sukhībala --a son of Nṛcakṣu (Tricakṣu-Vā. P.), (Nṛpacakṣu-Vi. P.) and father of Pāriplava. M. 50. 82; Vā. 99. 274; Vi. IV. 21. 12.

सुखोदय
Sukhodaya --a son of Medhātithi and founder of the Sukhodayam kingdom (Sukhānu kingdom in Plakṣadvīpa). Br. II. 14. 36-8; Vā. 33. 32; Vi. II. 4. 4 and 5.

