Sukhodayam --a varṣa adjoining the Nārada hill of Plakṣa; 1) Br. II. 14. 38; 19. 15; Vā. 49. 14; same as the Kaumāram. 2) M. 122. 22.

सुगति
Sugati --a son of Gaya and Gāyantī. Bhā. V. 15. 14.

