Saindhavāyana --read Atharva Samhitā with Babhru from Śuneka; a pupil of Śaunaka. Bhā. XII. 7. 3; Br. II. 35. 60.

सैन्धवायन
Saindhavāyanas --a Kauśika clan; 1) Br. III. 66. 74. Trayārṣeya. 2) M. 198. 4.

