Sainya --an army of four-fold forces and of six limbs; a nuisance to peace. Br. III. 26. 52-3; 27. 12-13; 38. 18; 48. 7. 

सैन्याति
Sainyāti --a Pravara Ṛṣi. M. 199. 15.

